<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="PTM8.2.3">
<l>aruvicōr vēṅkaṭam nīrmalai yeṉṟuvāy</l>
<l>veruviṉāḷ meyyam viṉaviyi rukkiṉṟāḷ</l>
<l>perukucīrk kaṇṇa purameṉṟu pēciṉāḷ</l>
<l>urukiṉā ḷuḷmelin tāḷitu veṉkolō.</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>She opened her mouth, saying, “Nīrmalai! Vēṅkaṭam</l>
<l>Where cascades flow!” She continues asking about Meyyam.</l>
<l>She spoke, saying, “Kaṇṇapuram of growing fame!”</l>
<l>[And] she languished; she has suffered in her heart. What is this?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
